data.meta_description: Free map of Haan, Germany  from FreeCountryMaps.com. Downloadable maps for use on school projects or to show your location within Germany. The map page also includes the latitude and longitude of Haan as well as its population and location in  Germany
data.text:
Map of Haan, Germany

Please note that the first map is a static map of Haan, Germany provided by Openstreetmap, it is free to copy, modify and use as per their terms of use. Right click on the map of Haan to save your free map of Haan, Germany.

I have also added a Google Map showing the location of Haan, Germany which can be found below the free street map.

I will be making this map clickable so you can zoom in and out and add a marker to your location, place of business etc.
